strategies.title: CAHOLD
strategies.description: Close above the high of the low day
strategies.rules: 1 - Must be in a sideways or up trend | 2 - Must break resistance | 3 - Must have a small market cap ($250 million - $2 billion) | 4 - Must have a spike in traded shares following  or on day of CAHOLD

strategies.title: 50/20 SMA Crossover
strategies.description: 20 day SMA crosses over 50 day SMA trendline.
strategies.rules:
1 - Must be in a sideways or up trend
| 2 - Must be approaching an earnings report or recently had a good earnings report or news release
| 3 - Must have a small market cap  ($250 million - $2 billion)
| 4 - Must have a spike in traded shares following crossover

journalEntries.notes: Recent positive earnings report, up trending, trade spike day of CAHOLD, convergence of 20 day and 50 day SMA, but no crossover yet.
